QuestData.Title: Disrupting the Flow
QuestData.Description: You there, we need to stop the flow of demon reinforcements!$B$BDo you see the floating fel crystals spread throughout the front? Those resonators are powering the portals unleashing hell on our forces. I need you to take them out!
QuestData.LogDescription: Destroy $1oa Burning Resonators in the Burning Front.
QuestData.RewardText: We can take it from here. Light's blessings to you, $c.
